99-0562 (La. 4/23/99)

STATE of Louisiana v. Charles RODRIGUEZ. No. 99-KD-0562. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: Rodriguez; Charles; — Defendants); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs; Parish of Tangipahoa 21st Judicial District Court Div. “A” Number 84077; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, Number KW99 0455

Denied.

MARCUS, J. not on panel. JOHNSON, J. would grant the writ.
